dialogue.text: You like my outfit, baby? I bought this at Limited 22 when we was at the mall.
Oh shit, haha. Jasmine's sorry for making a mess on your lips, its been a while since we kissed.
Oh man, you're making Jasmine feel butterflies down there... lemme just.. take these off-
Ay Dios mio, papi... I don't wanna sing no mo. I wanna sing on your d-
Jeez fine, papi. I'll sing one more stupid ass song with you. Jasmine ain't holding back...
Then we can finally use this afterwards..mmm
